          -               -      GND |       | GND      -             -
 PWM11_M1 - UART4_M1_CTS  - GPIO1_C7 |       | 3V3_EN   -             -
 PWM10_M1 - UART4_M1_RTS  - GPIO1_C6 |       | 3V3_OUT  -             -
 PWM9_M1  - UART4_M1_TX   - GPIO1_C5 |       | NC       -             -
